11#ifndef API_AUDIO_CODECS_L16_AUDIO_DECODER_L16_H_
12#define API_AUDIO_CODECS_L16_AUDIO_DECODER_L16_H_
13
14#include <memory>
15#include <vector>
16
17#include "absl/types/optional.h"
18#include "api/audio_codecs/audio_codec_pair_id.h"
19#include "api/audio_codecs/audio_decoder.h"
20#include "api/audio_codecs/audio_format.h"
21#include "rtc_base/system/rtc_export.h"
22
23namespace webrtc {
24
25// L16 decoder API for use as a template parameter to
26// CreateAudioDecoderFactory<...>().
27struct RTC_EXPORT AudioDecoderL16 {
28 struct Config {
29 bool IsOk() const {
30 return (sample_rate_hz == 8000 || sample_rate_hz == 16000 ||
31 sample_rate_hz == 32000 || sample_rate_hz == 48000) &&
32 num_channels >= 1;
33 }
34 int sample_rate_hz = 8000;
35 int num_channels = 1;
36 };
37 static absl::optional<Config> SdpToConfig(const SdpAudioFormat& audio_format);
38 static void AppendSupportedDecoders(std::vector<AudioCodecSpec>* specs);
39 static std::unique_ptr<AudioDecoder> MakeAudioDecoder(
40 const Config& config,
41 absl::optional<AudioCodecPairId> codec_pair_id = absl::nullopt);
42};
43
44} // namespace webrtc
45
46#endif // API_AUDIO_CODECS_L16_AUDIO_DECODER_L16_H_
